data.description: MOTIVATED SELLER! BRING ALL OFFERS!  Beautiful 4 bedroom, 3 bath home with an office that can be converted into another bedroom. Open kitchen ties into the family room and features granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, double ovens, gas cooktop, large island, and custom upgraded cabinets with loads of storage space! The large formal dining area, in addition to the eat-in kitchen area, provides plenty of space for entertaining. The open living area features large windows viewing the back yard and upgraded fire place with beautiful trim. The primary bedroom has room for seating and an spacious bathroom with double sinks, garden tub, separate shower with bench, and a large walk-in closet. The upstairs game room is great for a family game night or just lounging on the couch with easy access to the media room tied into this area.  The upgraded back porch is sure to create an oasis for you with extended decking along with a gas hookup for any grilling needs.
